libcgi-conduit-perl (0.07) lucid; urgency=low

  * We _do_ get in there, so set the 'keywords' to nothing and set the proper key to the empty string
  * Use the newer get_dbh() rather than the deprecated get_pg() (will require more work)
  * Update session_set() to just take a new session
  * Prepare for new release of Conduit
  * Pass the captures to the before and after triggers
  * New directories for amalthea
  * Minor syntax fix (added semi-colon)
  * Minor fix in POD
  * Get a parameter as a list, no matter how many values it already holds
  * Fix up error handling when the file isn't there
  * Allow easy file downloads and rendering
  * Add the File module for easy access to uploaded files
  * Add a useful 403 status code helper

 -- Andrew Chilton <chilts@appsattic.com>  Sat, 08 Jan 2011 17:02:50 +1300

